- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of synthetic data to improve the performance of a neural machine translation model. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper deals with training a machine learning model for translation. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of a neural machine translation model. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss the use of image or video data in the translation task.
